# Kıvılcım - Turkish Autism Education Platform

**Platform:** Otizmli çocukların gelişimini destekleyen 10 aktif modül içeren eğitim platformu  
**Technologies:** Next.js 15 + React 19 + TypeScript + ElevenLabs + Firebase  
**Language:** Turkish primary with special autism-friendly design  
**Status:** 🟢 Production Ready (95%+ test coverage, 10 active modules)

## 🎯 Core Project Context

### Platform Status
- **10 Active Modules:** All educational modules functional and accessible
- **Gender-Balanced Voice System:** 3 erkek + 2 kadın sesli dengeli Türkçe sistem
- **Audio Priority:** Static MP3 files → ElevenLabs SDK → API Route → Web Speech API fallback
- **Test Coverage:** 95%+ maintained with comprehensive E2E and unit tests
- **Accessibility:** WCAG 2.1 AA compliant for autism spectrum disorders

### Key Files
- `lib/elevenlabs.ts` - Enhanced gender-balanced voice system
- `lib/audio-constants.ts` - Dialog mappings and audio file paths
- `dialog.md` - 94+ Turkish dialogs catalog
- `app/exercise/*/` - 10 educational modules (including mathematics, alphabet reading)
- `.cursor/rules/` - Complete centralized rule system (12 rule files)
- `docs/modules/` - Module-specific rule files (10 active modules)
- `prisma/schema.prisma` - Database schema with voice system integration
- `firestore.rules` - Firebase security rules for user data protection

### Current Issues (2025-01-07)
- **JSON Parse Error:** `app/modules/page.tsx` - SyntaxError: Unexpected end of JSON input
- **Favicon Conflict:** Duplicate favicon files causing 500 errors  
- **Font 404:** `/fonts/geist-sans.woff2` not found
- **CSS Entry Error:** entryCSSFiles undefined causing compilation issues
- **Server Port:** Running on 3002 (3000-3001 in use)
- **Metadata Warning:** metadataBase property not set for social images

### Active Module Paths
- `app/exercise/alphabet-reading/` - Alfabe okuma modülü (29 Turkish letters)
- `app/exercise/mathematics/` - Matematik dünyası modülü (1-10 numbers)
- `app/exercise/vocabulary/` - Kelime dağarcığı modülü (word matching)
- `app/exercise/social-communication/` - Sosyal iletişim modülü (emotion recognition)
- `app/exercise/writing-expression/` - Yazma ve ifade modülü (letter tracing)
- `app/exercise/basic-concepts/` - Temel kavramlar modülü (colors, shapes)
- `app/exercise/literacy/` - Okuryazarlık modülü (reading skills)
- `app/exercise/music-room/` - Müzik odası modülü (therapeutic music)
- `app/exercise/video-room/` - Video odası modülü (educational videos)
- `app/exercise/puzzle/` - Puzzle oyunu modülü (motor skills)

## 🔧 Technology Standards

### TypeScript Rules
- Strict mode enabled, NO `any` types
- Interfaces over types for object definitions
- Proper typing for ElevenLabs voice configurations
- Custom types for Turkish character handling

### React 19 + Next.js 15
- App Router exclusively (no Pages Router)
- Server Components by default, "use client" only when necessary
- Error boundaries for each module
- Suspense boundaries for loading states

### Context7 Documentation Integration
- **ALWAYS** use Context7 for external library documentation
- **MANDATORY** context7 calls before implementing new libraries
- Pattern: `mcp_context7_resolve-library-id` → `mcp_context7_get-library-docs`
- Focus on autism-friendly, accessible implementations
- Prioritize Turkish language support when available

### Gender-Balanced Voice System
```typescript
// Gender-balanced Turkish voice assignments
const VOICE_ASSIGNMENTS = {
  'letter': 'Adam',           // Male, calm and clear
  'word': 'Rachel',           // Female, professional 
  'sentence': 'Antoni',       // Male, storyteller tone
  'celebration': 'Josh',      // Male, energetic and fun
  'default': 'Gülsu'          // Female, consistency (Bella fallback)
};

// 4-tier fallback chain
async function playAudio(text: string, type: string) {
  try {
    // 1. Static MP3 file (preferred)
    return await playStaticAudio(text, type);
  } catch {
    // 2. ElevenLabs with gender-balanced assignment
    return await elevenLabsSpeak(text, VOICE_ASSIGNMENTS[type]);
  }
}
```

## 📋 Documentation Assistant

### Auto-Documentation Triggers
- **Feature discussions** → Update `docs/prd.md`
- **Error reports** → Create `docs/reports/FAIL-report-YYYYMMDD-HHMMSS.md`
- **Task mentions** → Update `docs/todo.md`
- **Audio issues** → Link to dialog system docs
- **Rule updates** → Update relevant `.cursor/rules/*.md` files

### Documentation Standards
- All content in Turkish
- Structured markdown format
- Proactive updates based on conversation context
- Autism-friendly clear language

## 🎨 Component Patterns

### Module Components
```typescript
interface ModuleProps {
  moduleId: string;
  title: string;
  isActive: boolean;
  onVoicePlay?: (text: string, type?: 'letter' | 'word' | 'sentence' | 'celebration') => void;
}

// Accessibility requirements
- Minimum 44px touch targets
- ARIA labels in Turkish
- Keyboard navigation support
- Color contrast 4.5:1 minimum
```

### Voice-Enabled Components
- Gender-balanced voice assignments by content type
- Immediate visual feedback for all audio interactions
- Graceful fallback to visual-only mode
- Turkish phoneme support (29-letter alphabet)

## 🧪 Testing Requirements

### Two-Tier Test Architecture
- **Development Tests:** Single browser (Chromium) for rapid feedback (~3 minutes)
- **Full Coverage Tests:** 7 browsers for cross-platform compatibility (~15 minutes)
- **Test Coverage:** 95%+ maintained across all modules
- **E2E Coverage:** All 10 modules with accessibility validation

### Performance Targets
- LCP < 2.5s
- FID < 100ms  
- CLS < 0.1
- Static audio usage > 70%

## 🔒 Security & Ethics

### API Security
- ElevenLabs keys server-side only
- Rate limiting: IP-based with 60 requests/minute
- Input validation for Turkish text
- Usage monitoring and logging

### Privacy & Autism Considerations
- GDPR/KVKK compliant data handling
- Sensory-friendly default settings
- Predictable interaction patterns
- Calm color palettes and minimal animations

## 📊 Development Priorities

### Current Focus (2025-01-07)
1. **Fix JSON Parse Error:** Resolve modules page compilation issues
2. **Favicon Conflict Resolution:** Remove duplicate favicon files
3. **Font Loading Fix:** Implement proper font loading strategy
4. **CSS Entry Files:** Fix entryCSSFiles undefined error
5. **Module Stability:** Ensure all 10 modules work consistently

### Quality Standards
- TypeScript strict mode enforcement
- ESLint + Prettier formatting
- Pre-commit hooks for quality checks
- 95%+ test coverage maintenance

---

**Core Principle:** Every development decision prioritizes accessibility, consistency, and positive user experience for children with autism spectrum disorders. Gender-balanced voice system provides diverse, reliable audio experiences essential for creating an inclusive learning environment.

